#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.linalg.solve.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.linalg.solve"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.solve.solve:1 of
msgid "Solve the equation ``a x = b`` for ``x``."
msgstr "求解方程 ``a x = b`` 中的 ``x``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.solve.solve of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.solve.solve:3 of
msgid "A square matrix."
msgstr "一个方阵。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.solve.solve:5 of
msgid "Right-hand side matrix in ``a x = b``."
msgstr "方程 ``a x = b`` 中的右端矩阵。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.solve.solve:7 of
msgid ""
"Assume `a` is symmetric and positive definite. If ``True``, use Cholesky "
"decomposition."
msgstr "假设 `a` 是对称正定矩阵。如果为 ``True``，则使用 Cholesky 分解。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.solve.solve:10 of
msgid "Return sparse value or not."
msgstr "是否返回稀疏值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.solve.solve of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.solve.solve:13 of
msgid ""
"* **x** (*(M,) or (M, N) ndarray*) * Solution to the system ``a x = b``."
"  Shape of the return matches the * shape of `b`."
msgstr ""
"* **x** (*(M,) 或 (M, N) ndarray*) * 方程 ``a x = b`` 的解。返回值的形状"
"与 `b` 的形状一致。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.solve.solve:13 of
msgid "**x** (*(M,) or (M, N) ndarray*)"
msgstr "**x** (*(M,) 或 (M, N) ndarray*)"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.solve.solve:14 of
msgid "Solution to the system ``a x = b``.  Shape of the return matches the"
msgstr "方程 ``a x = b`` 的解。返回值的形状与"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.solve.solve:15 of
msgid "shape of `b`."
msgstr "`b` 的形状一致。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.solve.solve of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.solve.solve:21 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.solve.solve:22 of
msgid "Given `a` and `b`, solve for `x`:"
msgstr "给定 `a` 和 `b`，求解 `x`："

